{"tw": {"2575040": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Mansion of Memories", "steam_appid": 2575040, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>🍒 ADD OUR NEW GAME TO YOUR WISHLIST 🍒</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/71cc81f96f2ae56f4ca7010cfcf40315.poster.avif?t=1772795936\" width=622 height=227 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/71cc81f96f2ae56f4ca7010cfcf40315.webm?t=1772795936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/0b66b3286d9fe713edbfc344552c96d1.avif?t=1772795936\" width=616 height=253 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你從未想過自己會身處這樣的境地。出乎意料的繼承權？一座充滿秘密的洋館？聽起來像是本哥特小說的情節。但是，你已經到達了這裡--- 這座古老的莊園之中，這座曾屬於你已故的姑姑 Ann Bloodworth 的莊園。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Mansion of Memories”是一部偵探主題的視覺小說。本遊戲的特色包括時髦的幻想生物，浪漫的感情線，和一絲絲的春色。你是一大筆可疑遺產的繼承人之一。你被邀請來到了這座陰暗的洋館，與你一同前來的還有其他幾人。而你們全都跟手頭這件事息息相關。而你將會把這一切查的水落石出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/b4ce1ab5bc8a64d3d9a80c47b260742f.avif?t=1772795936\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解開謎團，推進情節。但請記住，你的一切選擇都將對未來產生影響。為什麼管家的出現讓你如此不安？在上鎖的閣樓中傳來的腳步聲又隱藏著何種秘密？最讓人不寒而栗的是，要是你在遺產爭奪中快人一步，那麼為達目的不擇手段的 Margaret 又會做出何種極端的行為呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這次調查開啟了一次漫長而復雜的旅程，但是你將會找到能夠伴你左右的友人。有可能是勇於面對挑戰而又開朗的Liz，也有可能是身懷秘密的Felix… 前提是你能獲得他的青睞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >誰知道你能否在 Ann Bloodworth 的遺願之中收穫某種比友誼更深的聯繫呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/984cc070f9a7441776ba10c5d64bf0e6.avif?t=1772795936\" width=616 height=368 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 敘事豐富的經典偵探情節；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 各種各樣的任務；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 會產生蝴蝶效應的選擇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 讓人享受的愛情故事；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 美女和……別的美麗生靈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/c49c7d90af8470b91486a121ae679b1c.webp?t=1772795936\" width=612 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/3cf1a190106066adecbad491d031d179.webp?t=1772795936\" width=612 height=41 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2575040/extras/0b66b3286d9fe713edbfc344552c96d1.avif?t=1772795936\" width=616 height=253 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你從未想過自己會身處這樣的境地。出乎意料的繼承權？一座充滿秘密的洋館？聽起來像是本哥特小說的情節。但是，你已經到達了這裡--- 這座古老的莊園之中，這座曾屬於你已故的姑姑 Ann Bloodworth 的莊園。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Mansion of Memories”是一部偵探主題的視覺小說。本遊戲的特色包括時髦的幻想生物，浪漫的感情線，和一絲絲的春色。你是一大筆可疑遺產的繼承人之一。你被邀請來到了這座陰暗的洋館，與你一同前來的還有其他幾人。而你們全都跟手頭這件事息息相關。而你將會把這一切查的水落石出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><